song_name: Ruby Dont Take Your Love To Town
Ruby Dont Take Your Love To Town

version_description: Corrected and timed chords, lyrics, and intro tab, relevant theory notes and edits for readability.

In the key of the original on the album. Added timing to the intro riff (synth), and tried to space out the chords in the ending to make it easier to see the timing of the hits. Fixed a chord in Verse 2 that is the only different one (B as opposed to D#m) in any of the verses.
An intro was added. Some passing chords were added to make the song more melodic. Some of the chords were repositioned to be over the correct words.
This is in the correct key, with the correct words and phrases, you can transpose it as needed and add capos for those of you who can't sing along with the recording.
